729031f-a.title: Richmond: Jewett Avenue - New Street
729031f-a.text:
(1)
45 and 43 Jewett Avenue, east side, between New Street and Be
Street, showing,at No. 45, the Holy Redeemer Protestant Episcopa
Church (Italian). No. 43 is a 1-story house. The view is north
ward.
May 22, 1929
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The shrine in front of the church.
May 22, 1929
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
